---------------------------------------
- Submodules
---------------------------------------

This distribution use the following projects as GIT submodules:

    - Athena-Core
    - Athena-Math
    - V8
    - UnitTest++
    - XMake

To download them, do:

	$ git submodule init
	$ git submodule update


Compilation
-----------

It is recommended to compile the project in a separate folder. Here's how I do it:

	$ mkdir build
	$ cd build
	$ cmake ..
	$ make
